fields.title: Hello there!
fields.content:
#Try me!

This is a fully functional editor, so go ahead and take it for a spin. FYI:

1. The **menu on the top left** shows your notes and lets you create new ones.
2. The **buttons on the top right** let you switch between different display modes, including a distraction-free full screen mode.

[Sign up](http://localhost:8000/auth/signup/) to save your notes.
